FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FYork City currently sit two points
OL,7,Fclear of Rochdale at the top of the
OL,8,FNational League table with two games
OL,9,Fremaining and remarkably, they face
OL,10,Feach other on the final day of the
OL,11,Fseason a week on Saturday - in what
OL,12,Fcould be a straight shootout to become
OL,13,Fchampions.
OL,15,FSome may make historical comparisons
OL,16,Fto the War of the Roses, but this
OL,17,Fbattle also involves two Channel
OL,18,FIslands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FThat is because the Ogden family, who
OL,7,Fown Rochdale, lease the small private
OL,8,Fisland of Jethou, while York City co-
OL,9,Fowner Julie-Anne Uggla runs a hotel in
OL,10,FAlderney.
OL,12,FNeither realised the connection at
OL,13,Ffirst, but are pleased to be
OL,14,Frepresenting the Bailiwick of Guernsey
OL,15,Fon the UK sporting stage.
OL,17,FJulie-Anne explains: "For two football
OL,18,Fclub owners to be attracted to the
OL,19,Fmagical Channel Islands that we're
OL,20,Fboth lucky enough to live in, I'd love
OL,21,Fto meet them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,F"It makes me super proud that there's
OL,7,Ftwo families from the Channel Islands
OL,8,Fthat are committed to two amazing
OL,9,Fclubs.
OL,11,F"I've got a huge connection with
OL,12,FAlderney, I love it. It's my happy
OL,13,Fplace."
OL,15,FCameron Ogden adds: "It's interesting,
OL,16,Fa friend of mine pointed out the York
OL,17,Fowners lived in Alderney and our
OL,18,Fconnection to Guernsey through Jethou.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,F"Then I realised they own a hotel on
OL,7,FAlderney that my parents had been to
OL,8,Frecently ... so there's quite a few
OL,9,Fconnections in the end.
OL,11,F"Once people pointed it out, it's nice
OL,12,Fto think you're on 'side Guernsey' on
OL,13,Fthis particular match, so it adds to
OL,14,Fit but in the big scheme of things,
OL,15,Fwe're concentrating on the process and
OL,16,Fnot getting too ahead of ourselves."
OL,18,FWhen asked about comparing their club
OL,19,Fto the islands they call home, both
OL,20,Frecognised the importance of local
OL,21,Fpeople coming together.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FCameron says: "In terms of Guernsey
OL,7,Fand Rochdale, there's definitely a
OL,8,Fcommunity spirit that runs between
OL,9,Fboth of those places and I think
OL,10,Fpeople have a really strong bond to
OL,11,Fthose communities."
OL,13,FJulie-Anne adds: "Both have special
OL,14,Fplaces in my heart. I love Alderney,
OL,15,Fit's quirky, beautiful, calm, kind and
OL,16,Fcrazy, and I love York because it has
OL,17,Fthe most incredible community of
OL,18,Fpeople."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FThe pair would also be keen to build
OL,7,Fstronger ties between the Channel
OL,8,FIslands and their respective teams.
OL,10,FJulie-Anne says York is working
OL,11,Fclosely with Guernsey FC, where
OL,12,FBournemouth midfielder Alex Scott
OL,13,Fstarted his career, to develop a
OL,14,Frelationship between the two clubs,
OL,15,Fwhile Cameron says Rochdale would be
OL,16,Fopen to the possibility of a pre-
OL,17,Fseason friendly with The Green Lions.
OL,19,FBefore that though, there is the push
OL,20,Ffor automatic promotion and neither
OL,21,Fteam can afford to blink first.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FThe National League does have form for
OL,7,Fremarkable title races; in the 2022-23
OL,8,Fseason Wrexham came out on top with a
OL,9,Fdivision record of 111 points, while
OL,10,FNotts County had to settle for second
OL,11,Fon 107 - although they did eventually
OL,12,Fwin at Wembley to go up through the
OL,13,Fplay-offs.
OL,15,FHowever, even they did not face each
OL,16,Fother on the final day of regular
OL,17,Fmatches.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FCameron says: "York were out-and-out
OL,7,Ffavourites from day one and it's
OL,8,Ffunny, someone pointed out that
OL,9,Ffixture way back in August and said it
OL,10,Fcould come down to this.
OL,12,F"I just couldn't quite believe it, so
OL,13,Fthe fact there's that possibility is
OL,14,Fcrazy but two teams with over 100
OL,15,Fpoints is mad."
OL,17,FJulie-Anne adds: "When you have two
OL,18,Fteams that are above 100 points, it's
OL,19,Fa tragedy that we're both not going up
OL,20,F(automatically).
OL,26,@|D@Apm|D@Opn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,F"No matter what happens between now
OL,7,Fand 25 April when we play against
OL,8,Fthem, my biggest hope is that we both
OL,9,Fgo up and the Rochdale owners and I
OL,10,Fthrow a huge party in the Channel
OL,11,FIslands celebrating together."
OL,13,FMuch has been made of the push for a
OL,14,F'three-up, three down' model but the
OL,15,Fclubs in the divisions above have to
OL,16,Fapprove it - which is rather like
OL,17,F'turkeys voting for Christmas' as it
OL,18,Fcreates another relegation spot from
OL,19,FLeague Two.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776787870
OL,3,CChannel Islands' football owners on
OL,4,Crace to reach the Football League
OL,6,FSo until something changes, it is the
OL,7,Fglory of becoming champions or the
OL,8,Flottery of the play-offs - Cameron and
OL,9,FJulie-Anne do not have long to wait
OL,10,Fbefore they find out their team's
OL,11,Ffate, and who will be popping that
OL,12,Fchampagne.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
